*       ╓─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╖
*       ║                                                         ║
*       ║                   APPSCX Cleanup Code                   ║
*       ║                                                         ║
*       ╙─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╜
*

#REGION 1
SET TALK OFF
* Cleanup code to construct CDX file and start the application
m.scxname = ALLTRIM(UPPER(m.scxname))
m.dbfname = ALLTRIM(UPPER(m.dbfname))
IF !FILE(m.scxname)
   WAIT WINDOW "The screen file is missing" NOWAIT
   CLOSE ALL
   CANCEL
ENDIF
IF !FILE(m.dbfname)
   WAIT WINDOW "The database file is missing" NOWAIT
   CLOSE ALL
   CANCEL
ENDIF

* Invert the database if there isn't a CDX file present already
m.invstem = juststem(m.dbfname)
m.cdxname = forceext(m.dbfname,'CDX')
IF FILE(m.cdxname)
   IF USED(m.invstem)
      SELECT (m.invstem)
   ELSE
      SELECT 0
      USE (LOCFILE(m.dbfname,'DBF','Locate '+m.dbfname+' please'))
   ENDIF
   IF RECCOUNT() = 0
      APPEND BLANK
   ENDIF
ELSE
   DO invert WITH m.dbfname
ENDIF

CLEAR WINDOW

GOTO TOP
CLEAR

RELEASE scxname, dbfname, invname, cdxname
CLOSE DATABASES

DEFINE WINDOW appdoc FROM 4,8 TO 16,73 COLOR SCHEME 5
ACTIVATE WINDOW appdoc
SET TEXTMERGE WINDOW appdoc
